    "In addition, developing more advanced representation learning methods may help capture the underlying structure of these relationships and improve the model's ability to learn from complex and variable data.",
    "Artificial intelligence is reshaping the research landscape for both olfactory (smell) and gustatory (taste) modalities.",
    "By utilizing big data analytics and machine learning techniques, AI enables deeper insights into sensory experiences.",
    "As shown in Table 3, a range of studies illustrates how AI is applied across olfactory and gustatory research, highlighting both shared methodologies and unique challenges in each field.",
